RADS Error: Could not connect to the HTTP server. Please check that your Internet connection is enabled and that your firewall is not blocking access.
I did a lot of research, tried almost every method on the internet, but none of them works, including: change IPv4 DNS (then cmd clear DNS cache), disable IPv6, close firewall, close anti-virus software, reset all network setting, reinstall the game, restart the PC, change system.cfg under RADS/system, etc. btw, I haven't play for a long time, just download it last night, but untill now, it's been that problem all the time.
Who can save me - -{{summoner:3}}
